  <p><a id="TSJN-01-03-0067-kw-0001" class="keywordref" title="jump to The proceedings of the council in text" href="#TSJN-01-03-0067-ks-0001">The proceedings of the council</a>: See <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-02-02-0125" class="document">the Councils Order, 16 June 1779</a>, above; on the Hamilton case generally, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-02-02-0118" class="document">TJ to Bland, 8 June 1779</a>. TJs <a id="TSJN-01-03-0067-kw-0002" class="keywordref" title="jump to letter in text" href="#TSJN-01-03-0067-ks-0002">letter</a> <a href="default.xqy?keys=TSJN-print-01-03-02-0057" class="document">acknowledged in the postscript was dated 23, not 19, July</a>, and is printed above.</p></div>
